QuestData.Title: Waste of Thyme
QuestData.Description: Living Ire Thyme. I must have more! Be quick about it, will you?
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 8 bundles of Living Ire Thyme near the Ruins of Nordressa.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do you have that thyme for me?
QuestData.RewardText: Perfect. It's quite interesting how useful the most random things end up being to incantations of this sort.$B$BSo much more to learn!
